## 15. How to Reproduce

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
./scripts/benchmark3000.sh
```

### Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `MAX_PARALLEL` | 4 | Parallel git clone jobs |
| `SCAN_TIMEOUT` | 300 | Per-project scan timeout (seconds) |
